        IGET Vapes Original is Australia's #1 trusted <strong>online vape shop</strong>, specialising in genuine disposable vapes from leading brands including IGET and Alibarbar. We launched with a simple mission: to give Australian customers a reliable, safe and affordable way to <strong>buy vapes online</strong> without the hassle of searching for "vape shops near me" or visiting unreliable stores.
