        <li><strong><a href="/products/iget-bar-pro">IGET Bar Pro 10000 Puffs</a></strong> — Australia's favourite disposable vape with 26 incredible flavours.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/iget-bar-plus-s3">IGET Bar Plus S3 10000 Puffs</a></strong> — Refillable pod system for vapers who prefer flexibility.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/iget-bar-plus-s3-pod">S3 Pod Replacements</a></strong> — Affordable replacement pods starting from just $30.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/alibarbar-ingot">Alibarbar Ingot 9000 Puffs</a></strong> — Compact design with rich Alibarbar flavours.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/products/alibarbar-ice-adjust">Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000 Puffs</a></strong> — Adjustable ice intensity for a personalised vaping experience.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Thousands of Australians Choose Us</h2>
