        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">100% Genuine Products</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Every IGET vape and Alibarbar vape is sourced from authorised distributors. No fakes, guaranteed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">150+ Vape Flavours</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">From Strawberry Watermelon to Cherry Pomegranate, Cool Mint to Orange Fanta Soda — we have every flavour.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fast Australia-Wide Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">We ship to Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, Adelaide, Gold Coast, Canberra, Hobart, Darwin and all regional areas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
